    "heading": "root-skillmd",
    "content": "If a plugin has no `skills/` directory and no `skills` field in the manifest, tools MAY treat a `SKILL.md` file at the plugin root as a single-skill plugin. The skill name is derived from the plugin name. This is a convenience for simple single-skill plugins."
