    "heading": "environment-variables",
    "content": "For cross-tool compatibility, tools SHOULD expand both `${PLUGIN_ROOT}` and their vendor-specific placeholder. Plugin authors targeting a single tool MAY use that tool's placeholder. Plugin authors targeting multiple tools SHOULD use `${PLUGIN_ROOT}` or provide both:"
